Description: DMRsegal implements a method for identifying Differentially 
    Methylated Regions (DMRs) from pre-computed Differentially Methylated 
    Positions (DMPs). The package uses a correlation-based approach to 
    expand regions around significant DMPs, considering both statistical 
    significance and biological relevance of methylation changes. It supports 
    standard beta value files and methylation bed files for efficient 
    processing of large datasets.
